E2F1BAU.original: ~z~Yo, H, I'm sorry, but life don't quite work that way. Stay safe, okay?
E2F1BAU.translated: ~z~哟，H，对不起，但计划还是赶不上变化。注意安全，好吗？

E2F1BAU.original: ~z~You could be right, bro. Other than this shipment we being paid to oversee, there ain't nothing else coming in for us.
E2F1BAU.translated: ~z~好像是这样，兄弟。除了一个收了钱的护卫任务，我们暂时也没别的活了。

E2F1BAU.original: ~z~Alright bro, I was young. I was stupid. But more importantly you getting any toto yourself at the moment?
E2F1BAU.translated: ~z~行了兄弟。那会儿我还小，很傻逼。不过现在你们都有女人了吗？

E2F1BAU.original: ~z~I'd let that bitch abuse the shit outta me right now. Oh yeah.
E2F1BAU.translated: ~z~我现在倒想让那婊子把我虐出屎来。哦耶。

E2F1BAU.original: ~z~Yo. You know I said I wouldn't get involved in that no more. I'll have to think about it, bro.
E2F1BAU.translated: ~z~哟，我说过再也不掺和这种事了。我得好好想想，兄弟。

E2F1BAU.original: ~z~We was just close friends. Whatever anyone told you is fucking bullshit, man. Fucking bullshit!
E2F1BAU.translated: ~z~他就是我一哥们儿。别人说的那些都他妈是扯淡，兄弟。全他妈扯淡！

E2F1BAU.original: ~z~We need to get those guys up there.
~z~Yo, man, that don't mean nothing. What you know about women anyway? Carmen's sweet.
E2F1BAU.translated: ~z~哟，哥们，这又没什么。你懂什么女人？Carmen很棒的。

E2F1BAU.original: ~z~Luis fucked Miss Adams, we had her in eighth.
E2F1BAU.translated: ~z~Luis操过Adams老师，八年级带我们的那个。

E2F1BAU.original: ~z~We got a minor problem with this door. Hold on.
E2F1BAU.translated: ~z~车门一时半会儿打不开，等下。

E2F1BAU.original: ~z~Turn they own weaponry against them, bro.
~z~There's enough chumps out there to do that work for you. Just get involved in the high level shit.
E2F1BAU.translated: ~z~随便找个白痴就能替你们派货，别在底层给人打工了。

E2F1BAU.original: ~z~Let's get the fuck out of here. Come on.
~z~Thanks, Luis. We'll see you soon, yeah.
~z~Them guys is still on the roof.
~z~Motherfucking coppers! H cover them guys on the left. I got these guys down here.
E2F1BAU.translated: ~z~操他妈的条子！H，你打左边那些，我对付这边。

E2F1BAU.original: ~z~Well shit did fuck up and I nearly got killed so I think I earned the right to be heard for a second.
E2F1BAU.translated: ~z~但确实出岔子了，我也差点没命。所以我应该有权利让你们听我说话。

E2F1BAU.original: ~z~I am sorry that I ain't a drug dealer no more. A friend of yours made something of his self.
E2F1BAU.translated: ~z~我不当毒贩了对不起啊。你的这个朋友有自己的成就。

E2F1BAU.original: ~z~I hear you nailed your technique on that last bid upstate, A.
E2F1BAU.translated: ~z~听说你上次坐过牢后可是大有长进。

E2F1BAU.original: ~z~I had to cut that girl loose, bro. You're lucky I did, otherwise you wouldn't be getting shit right now.
E2F1BAU.translated: ~z~我只能跟她分手，兄弟。幸好我跟她分了，否则你压根就操不到她。

E2F1BAU.original: ~z~We were running from the police when we was sixteen years old.
E2F1BAU.translated: ~z~十六岁大的时候我们就在躲警察了。

E2F1BAU.original: ~z~I should never have invited you along, bro. You is too used to the good life to get shit done now days.
E2F1BAU.translated: ~z~我就不该叫你来的，兄弟。你现在小日子过习惯了，干不了粗活了。

E2F1BAU.original: ~z~L, man, here you go. Take that bitch down. You was always the best shot.
E2F1BAU.translated: ~z~L，兄弟，拿好了，把她打下来。你一直是神枪手。

E2F1BAU.original: ~z~Sure am. Nice little girl by the name of Carmen Ortiz, lives out in So Bo.
E2F1BAU.translated: ~z~当然有。一个叫Carmen Ortiz的小美女，住在South Bohan。
~z~操你妈的。那会儿我才三年级。

E2F1BAU.original: ~z~Let's go! Let's go! We screwed if we stay here.
~z~One of us needs to get them guys up there.
E2F1BAU.translated: ~z~得有人把屋顶上的条子干掉。

E2F1BAU.original: ~z~Okay. Let's get back to the Heights.
~z~Ohhhhhh! Luis got his panties in a twist.
~z~Henrique bro, get these cops down here. I'll hold the ones on the left.
E2F1BAU.translated: ~z~Henrique兄弟，你打这边的条子。我打左边的。

E2F1BAU.original: ~z~I ain't getting caught up in another narco bust. Fuck!
E2F1BAU.translated: ~z~我不会再被缉毒队抓回去的，操！

E2F1BAU.original: ~z~You gonna listen to me or what? You never going to get anywhere if you guys are the ones selling on the corner.
E2F1BAU.translated: ~z~你到底听不听我讲话？在路边派货是出不了头的。

E2F1BAU.original: ~z~How the fuck we gonna get rid of this thing? Check the NOOSE van, L. They might be something in there.
E2F1BAU.translated: ~z~这他妈要怎么打？看看NOOSE的车，L。里面说不定有武器。

E2F1BAU.original: ~z~Oh shit! You did, didn't you? I wouldn't go making no piss jokes, A.
E2F1BAU.translated: ~z~哦操！真尿了啊？我就不开这种尿裤子的玩笑了，A。

E2F1BAU.original: ~z~What the fuck, man? We was always meant to protect that dumb bastard.
E2F1BAU.translated: ~z~这他妈咋了，哥们？保护这傻子明明是我们的职责。

E2F1BAU.original: ~z~That wasn't blood running down your leg, bro. You just wet yourself.
E2F1BAU.translated: ~z~你腿上沾的不是血，兄弟。你尿了而已。

E2F1BAU.original: ~z~Ain't that what you do at them clubs of yours?
~z~Shit, bro. Mando. Who gonna tell his moms?
~z~You was a victim of child abuse , you sick fuck.
E2F1BAU.translated: ~z~你是虐童的受害者，你个傻逼。

E2F1BAU.original: ~z~Shit, bro. I got these guys to the left. Henrique, go left, motherfucker.
E2F1BAU.translated: ~z~操，兄弟。左边来人了。Henrique，快来左边，妈了个逼的。

E2F1BAU.original: ~z~They ain't exactly gonna call up five-0 are they?
~z~Yo L, we holding these guys. Get behind the car and take out the NOOSE guys on the roof.
E2F1BAU.translated: ~z~哟，L，我们拖住他们。你躲到车后对付房顶上的NOOSE。

E2F1BAU.original: ~z~We asked you along to look pretty.
~z~Blow that motherfucker down, bro. Gimme a minute.
E2F1BAU.translated: ~z~那就炸出一条路，兄弟。我准备下。

E2F1BAU.original: ~z~Who hasn't had this piece of ass?
~z~Yeah, I ain't lecturing. I'm just looking out for my boys.
E2F1BAU.translated: ~z~喂，我没在讲课，是在关心兄弟。

E2F1BAU.original: ~z~This thing is holding us down, bro. Check that motherfucking NOOSE van. See if they got something can help.
E2F1BAU.translated: ~z~直升机在跑不了，兄弟。看看傻逼NOOSE的卡车，说不定有能用上的家伙。

E2F1BAU.original: ~z~Who'd a thought the NOOSE would be packing one of these.
E2F1BAU.translated: ~z~谁能想到NOOSE会带着这玩意行动。

E2F1BAU.original: ~z~but me and Rique are gonna need to do some serious work if we gonna maintain shit on these streets.
E2F1BAU.translated: ~z~但我和Rique还想接着在道上混的话就得干几票大的。

E2F1BAU.original: ~z~We didn't know shit was gonna fuck up.
~z~It must be a real disappointment to you. See you around, yeah?
E2F1BAU.translated: ~z~你一定很失望吧。再见了，好吗？

E2F1BAU.original: ~z~Ortiz? Shit, how come I know that name? She a nurse?
E2F1BAU.translated: ~z~Ortiz？操，这名字好耳熟啊。是护士吗？

E2F1BAU.original: ~z~Putting him to work on a corner don't seem much like protecting him to me man. I'm out.
E2F1BAU.translated: ~z~我不觉得让他去路边贩毒是保护他，哥们。我走了。

E2F1BAU.original: ~z~Throw some pineapples in the mix, bro.
~z~That all well and good, bro. But selling ain't our issue. It's getting hold of product.
E2F1BAU.translated: ~z~确实很有道理，兄弟。但销售不成问题，重点是找到货源。

E2F1BAU.original: ~z~You got to get behind that car and deal with those NOOSE boys on the roof, L. Me and H is holding here.
E2F1BAU.translated: ~z~你躲到车后面对付房顶上的NOOSE，L。我和H在这里拖延。

E2F1BAU.original: ~z~We need to get out of here, bro. We fucked if we stick around.
E2F1BAU.translated: ~z~我们得赶紧出去，兄弟。待在原地就完了。

E2F1BAU.original: ~z~I'm cool, L. I thought for a second they mighta shot my freaking balls off.
E2F1BAU.translated: ~z~我没事，L。不过我差点以为蛋被打爆了。

E2F1BAU.original: ~z~I'll do that, bro. You better lay low. Cops might want to ask you questions when they identify him.
E2F1BAU.translated: ~z~我去吧，兄弟。你低调点。条子查到他的身份后多半会来找你。

E2F1BAU.original: ~z~You run Tony's shit, do you? Where's the money then?
~z~Thanks, bro. Me and Rique mighta been fucked up if you weren't around for us.
E2F1BAU.translated: ~z~谢了兄弟。要不是有你在，我跟Rique可能就被抓了。

E2F1BAU.original: ~z~Let's hustle, boys. We got to get gone ASAP.
E2F1BAU.translated: ~z~快点冲，哥们。我们得尽快撤退。

E2F1BAU.original: ~z~We ain't moving with that thing there. See if there's something we can take it out with in that NOOSE van.
E2F1BAU.translated: ~z~直升机在我们跑不掉的。看看NOOSE的卡车里面有没有能用的装备。

E2F1BAU.original: ~z~We could use someone we can trust.
~z~Luis bro, you want us to come downtown to lecture you on interior decoration?
E2F1BAU.translated: ~z~Luis，兄弟，你要咱们去城里教你室内装修吗？

E2F1BAU.original: ~z~He's a good guy, got three kids.
~z~Thanks for the lecture, professor. I didn't know a two year stretch qualified you to teach Street Life 101.
E2F1BAU.translated: ~z~说得太好了，教授。没想到你进号子蹲了两年，出来都能教我们黑社会入门了。

E2F1BAU.original: ~z~Them guys on the roof is yours, L. Get behind the car and handle them. Me and Rique will hold position.
E2F1BAU.translated: ~z~房顶上的家伙你负责，L。躲到车后干了他们。我和Rique守这边。

E2F1BAU.original: ~z~Fuck you. You insane? She was our third grade teacher.
E2F1BAU.translated: ~z~滚你妈的，你有病吧？她是我们的三年级老师。

E2F1BAU.original: ~z~Fuck me, bro. The NOOSE is some well equipt motherfuckers.
E2F1BAU.translated: ~z~我操，兄弟。NOOSE的傻逼真的是武装到牙齿。

E2F1BAU.original: ~z~At least I didn't abandon him for some rich downtown assholes. Fuck off.
E2F1BAU.translated: ~z~至少我没为了城里的哪个阔佬就抛弃他。你滚吧。

E2F1BAU.original: ~z~Oh shit! Oh shit! Where A at?
~z~Shit. Let's get in that car and go.
~z~And never talk on the motherfucking phone.
~z~Blow these fucks up, bro. You got grenades.
E2F1BAU.translated: ~z~炸翻这些臭逼，兄弟。你有手雷。

E2F1BAU.original: ~z~What are you talking about? There's product all over the city. Just take it off motherfuckers.
E2F1BAU.translated: ~z~你说什么呢？城里最多的不就是货？找个冤大头就是了。

E2F1BAU.original: ~z~Look. As you say, I ain't an expert in this shit, but I do run a business.
E2F1BAU.translated: ~z~听着。如你所说，我不是道上的专家，但我确实在做生意。

E2F1BAU.original: ~z~Rique! We got a wall, bro. Do something about it.
~z~Shit. Yeah. Ummm... we had this thing about a year ago. She kinda nasty, bro.
E2F1BAU.translated: ~z~操。对，呃...我们一年前认识的。她有点放荡，兄弟。

E2F1BAU.original: ~z~The Jingoism Act, that shit means they can pretty much read your thoughts now and get away with it.
E2F1BAU.translated: ~z~沙文主义法案，就是说他们想查你的信息就查你的信息。

E2F1BAU.original: ~z~Fuck! Rique, bro, pop test. What you do when you got cops behind you and a dead end in front?
E2F1BAU.translated: ~z~操！Rique，兄弟，我考考你。后有追兵前无出路该怎么办？

E2F1BAU.original: ~z~We ain't getting out of here with her pinning us down like this. Take this and get her out the sky, shooter.
E2F1BAU.translated: ~z~被她这样咬着咱是跑不掉的。拿这个把她从天上打下来，射手。

E2F1BAU.original: ~z~Get these assholes with a grenade, man.
~z~I don't see why you guys are giving me shit. You was the ones who asked me to come along on this thing.
E2F1BAU.translated: ~z~你们没事找我麻烦干嘛？这次就是你把我拖下水的。

E2F1BAU.original: ~z~We got reinforcements dropped in up there.
~z~Them Annihilators make me real uncomfortable, bro. Come on.
E2F1BAU.translated: ~z~歼灭者搞得我是真的难受，兄弟。赶紧打。

E2F1BAU.original: ~z~This don't look good, L. Can you take this and try to sink the chopper. I don't trust my aim.
E2F1BAU.translated: ~z~情况不太妙啊，L。你能拿这个把直升机打下来吗？我准头不大好。

E2F1BAU.original: ~z~He looks out for boys in tight denim shorts.
~z~We might just have to start ripping people off. You gonna help us?
E2F1BAU.translated: ~z~我们说不定是该开始抢货了。你会帮我们吗？

E2F1BAU.original: ~z~Oh yeah sabes que, Now that you mention it, I could do with some dick sucking lessons.
E2F1BAU.translated: ~z~哦，是吗，你这么一说，我觉得是得跟你学学怎么口人。

E2F1BAU.original: ~z~Oh yeah. I forgot about that. What can I say man, I was the star pupil.
E2F1BAU.translated: ~z~是吗。我都快忘了。我能怎么办呢，我可是尖子生。

E2F1BAU.original: ~z~Demolitions! We got us a dead end. You ready?
E2F1BAU.translated: ~z~拆了它！前面没路了。准备好没？

E2F1BAU.original: ~z~Yo Armando, you got to be careful of them phones, man. People are onto that shit.
E2F1BAU.translated: ~z~喂，Armando，以后打电话多长点心眼，哥们。政府都盯着的。

E2F1BAU.original: ~z~Thanks, bro. You know I hate to ask this now you all Johnny lawful and shit,
E2F1BAU.translated: ~z~谢了兄弟。你现在是守法公民，我也不太想拉你下水。

E2F1BAU.original: ~z~Ain't gonna be a there much longer, bro.
~z~That wasn't good, bro. I thought we was gonna be rich after today.
E2F1BAU.translated: ~z~这可不好啊，兄弟。我还以为过了今天我们就发财了。

E2F1BAU.original: ~z~Move that car, you idiot. I got plans for that wall.
E2F1BAU.translated: ~z~到那辆车去，你个傻逼。对于那堵墙我有办法了。

E2F1BAU.original: ~z~Luis back on board, bro. I know it.
~z~So much for that package of yours.
~z~Yo, man. I don't know. I could do with the money but you boys is clowns.
E2F1BAU.translated: ~z~哟，兄弟。我不知道。给钱我就肯帮，但你俩有点菜。

E2F1BAU.original: ~z~Yo, A, I... ummm... I'm not sure about that.
~z~Mrs. Lebowitz? Didn't you go back and screw that bitch, L?
~z~Ten four trying to take us down. Get through them.
~z~Fuck, bro. We better not hang around. Let's get back to Northwood.
E2F1BAU.translated: ~z~操，兄弟。咱最好别在这瞎逛了，回Northwood吧。

E2F1BAU.original: ~z~I ain't letting them cops get H. We got to go back.
E2F1BAU.translated: ~z~不能让条子抓住H。快回去找他。

E2F1BAU.original: ~z~Whole load of work for nothing, bro. Fuck!
~z~I fucked her too, bro. She pretty nasty.
E2F1BAU.translated: ~z~我也上过她，兄弟。她是真的放荡。

E2F1BAU.original: ~z~We got to clear these fucks out, bro.
~z~Wait. This might take me a minute.
~z~Shit! You all alright, bros? No severe injuries back there?
E2F1BAU.translated: ~z~操！都没事吧，兄弟们？刚才没受重伤吧？

E2F1BAU.original: ~z~The chopper's back. Get out of here.
~z~I pissed myself, did I? You the one who couldn't hold it in in Mrs. Lebowitz's class?
E2F1BAU.translated: ~z~我是尿了，怎么？在Lebowitz老师的课上没憋住的是谁来着？

E2F1BAU.original: ~z~Alright, we better scram back to the Heights now.
~z~What you doing with that car, you weirdo? We might need to go through there.
E2F1BAU.translated: ~z~你个逗逼在车子那干啥呢？我们得穿过去。

E2F1BAU.original: ~z~Stuff don't seem to change with you two. I'll see you soon.
E2F1BAU.translated: ~z~看来你俩还是老样子啊。再见了。

E2F1BAU.original: ~z~Fuck. We got to get through these bitches.
